						               													<description>A stolen love, a business prejudice, an unforgivable mistake, &amp;hellip;  &amp;#10;You have so many reasons to seek revenge. And there are many demons that can give you this satisfaction...&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Resonance is a wicked game of observation and manipulation, set during a hazardous ritual of black magic.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Your quest for revenge has brought you this far, where the border of Hell is the most fragile. You will need a full lunar month to open a passage and summon the demon that will serve you.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;But you are not the only one to have had the idea of playing with the dark forces to achieve your purpose. Demonstrate skill, determination and of course spells to ensure the pursuit of your goals.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Resonance is a game for 3 to 8 witches which lasts about twenty minutes per game.&amp;#10;Game rounds are nothing more than the different phases of the Moon. Each phase of the Moon corresponds to a slot on the summoning circle, and you have Ritual Objects such as Herbs, Minerals and Potions to place on these 8 slots.&amp;#10;If the right combination of Ritual Objects resonates with the Moons, you pass one of the 3 steps required to summon your demon.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The first witch to complete the summoning ritual wins the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Play quickly to leave no respite to your opponents, carefully manipulate the course of this adventure and above all do not let victory escape you!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
